Film producer and writer Editi Effiong has opened up on being an atheist. Effiong, who is a producer of ‘Up North,’ took to his Twitter page to reveal his religious status. According to him, he would never go back to religion again.   No girl is a saint – Rapper Erigga     Female films, TV practitioners partner Ooni of Ife for…     Sean Dampte speaks on upcoming album   Read Also: Female films, TV practitioners partner Ooni of Ife for summit He stressed: “I’m probably never going back to religion but I could never shake the feeling that God is there. We are not cool but I’m willing to try,” he said. - Advertisement - “I lost my faith in 2020. Went through 2021 without God. Don’t invite me to your church abeg. And don’t preach in my mentions.”